description:
- Verdure Fishing Outfit "A breezy fishing-style outfit inspired by the verdure of early summer."
 - Kid's Verdure Fishing Outfit "A breezy fishing-style outfit for kids, inspired by the verdure of early summer."

 - Pink Hibiscus Mini Boater Hat "A small, fisherman-style straw hat adorned with a hibiscus flower."
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop( Fashion Store in Castle St. ) when you purchase it.
name: Verdure Fishing Outfit Set
